      <section eId="sec_4915">
        <num>4915</num>
        <heading>Prohibited practices</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  ยง 4915. Prohibited practices. An external appeal agent shall not, with\nrespect to external appeal activities, permit or provide compensation or\nanything of value to its employees, agents, or contractors based on:\n  1. either a percentage of the amount by which a claim is reduced for\npayment or the number of claims or the cost of services for which the\nperson has denied authorization or payment; or\n  2. any other method that encourages the upholding of an adverse\ndetermination.\n</p>
        </content>
      </section>
